{"tid":2107162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★bin c】【父親節】酒樓座無虛席 廢老：香港福地來的！","createTime":"2020-07-13T16:35:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T05:08:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a3d804497dca9a36e8f0a35bf52e71678b0e0cc","tid":2107162,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"上午10時，旺角的倫敦大酒樓已經人聲鼎沸，座無虛席。限聚令放寬後，酒樓已將12人的大枱搬出，不少大家庭亦前來光顧。黃先生一家十二人前來用餐，他說限聚令未放寬時，已經打提早預定座位「book咗先」。疫情以來，一家人已經數月未能一起出來聚餐，在父親節可以用餐，都覺得開心。此行家中不少親朋都來到，包括爺爺嫲嫲，黃爺爺就表示過往一家人在節日都會出來聚餐，「母親節未能出來，所以父親節出來。不過都會戴口罩，洗手，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">香港福地來的</span></strong>！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4tGhzU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4tGhzU.png&h=b5ff142b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f44f67add1df5db44fcb3198cf65f26db9b5386","tid":2107162,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fcf08b23b3ae2578f69e7d4ff78b9886ab4e84","tid":2107162,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73bb98a6b8e62c280b2adc3c2697ce535346703","tid":2107162,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T16:44:51.000Z","msg":"可以做電影題材<br />\n第一幕：影住電視講放寬防疫限制，主角WhatsApp 家庭group 約食父親節飯<br />\n第二幕：主角搭地鐵時，見到幾個支那人嘈喧巴閉，上前勸喻引發衝突，原來支那人有豁免檢疫證書，主角感染支那病毒<br />\n第三幕：去酒樓食飯，病毒周圍飛，爸爸說香港是福地，不要搞事<br />\n第四幕：社會大爆發，貧者一萬留一千，富者一萬留二三。<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"e4dcc6c55a3e9a2eacde83978a45b9dc13f1c887","tid":2107162,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:15:54.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"96d1b63da6cf5f19195b5cc33c6c1ab9b91b7df1","tid":2107162,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9b25e4611c785a412afd73ae68eaf3b238aded","tid":2107162,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:24:49.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心更新確診患者行蹤，新增19間食肆曾有確診者到訪。油尖旺區有數間餐廳上榜，包括尖沙咀中心Outback Steakhouse、南洋中心百樂門宴會廳、南洋中心富士山55 (拉麵沾麵專門店) 、<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>旺角倫敦大酒樓</strong></span>及旺角88。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96bfd4a540a795fbc59bfbad9fed9029e04e8763","tid":2107162,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}